name: Durgandini #2
description: Dewi Durgandini is very beautiful, but suffered from a rare skin illness that stinks. Literally, her skin smelled bad. Luckily, she recovered from that illness. Now Dewi Durgandini is not only beautiful, but also smells good. Her intoxicating aroma attracts the attention of all men. Dewi Durgandini also gets the nickname Dewi Sayojagahandi.
